'''Agerru''' d agraw neɣ d asemdi n tdusiyin n tukza am [[tanuggit|tnuggit]], [[Tamusni]], [[Aswingem]], [[Tanurnant]], [[Tagerrawt]], [[Taɣara]] d [[tutlayt]].
Agerru ila (yesɛa) tizmert di [[tasugint|tsugint]] d [[asemgerred|usemgerred]], Akken daɣen yella d amasay (imḍebber) af tɣuri n [[afray|wafrayen]].

== Assaɣ d wallaɣ ==
Tigzi n wassaɣ yellan gar n ugerru d [[alaɣ|wallaɣ]] d yiwet n taluft yellan d tadaslant deg umezruy n tfelsuft.
